(44, 13, 31, 44, 1, 11, 11, 'witnesses unto the people', 'Witnesses of Jesus'' Ascension', 'Both passages emphasize the witnesses of Jesus'' ministry and ascension. Acts 13:31 mentions those who saw Jesus after his resurrection, while Acts 1:11 refers to the men of Galilee witnessing his ascension.', 'theme', 0.321, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
